号，导致发射中止。经调查，检测到异常信号的原因是火箭第一级的 LE-9 主发动机电源系统出现异常。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-84ba75e30650f98fb01cec1901fb9428_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588030007"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIg8bKxNni0/k8EAMaCDkyOTU1MTMxIJy5mqAGMAo4hwFAHXIJNTg4MDMwMDA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1678183609.19723", "card_id": "Q_587294828", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "跨省抢工的汽车相关企业说「三到五年的计划已经做出来了，为了今后市场，准备扩厂招工」，如何看待这种判断？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上次「相对论」节目组跟着浙江的招工团去了劳务输出大县贵州三都，在回答里看到有知友聊到跨省抢工，「我们看到的是『抢人』、是招工、是服务、是高薪上门接人，『抢人』的背后是人们对经济复苏的期望。」 这种期望，特别珍贵。评论区里，不少知友聊到汽车行业，我就想起，在贵州三都县的招聘会上，遇到了一位汽车行业的招工代表。她说，公司做了一个「三到五年的计划」，预计「接下来汽车行业发展可能会比较好」，为了以后的市场，他们正在准备进一步扩厂，寻找一些有潜力的招工点，就是为扩厂做准备。 如何看待这种判断？你所在的行业，最新的增长点又在哪里？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d85f33f76d7835ff33bc72f496b55ae0_1440w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587294828"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIg8bKxNni0/k8EAMaCDkyNzkxNTkxIM7rhaAGMAA4UkAecgk1ODcyOTQ4Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1678183609.1979144", "card_id": "Q_587475976", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为啥 F1 也算体育运动？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "f1 拼的是机械和体育有多大关系，那我每天开车也算体育锻炼了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-b2b00b27bf3b725e12558bbc4161a85d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend",